cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.DB 

The paper discusses the privacy concerns related to the collection and analysis of real-time streaming data from sensors and actuators in intelligent infrastructure. This topic is closely related to the field of cybersecurity (cs.CR), as well as information retrieval (cs.IR) and data management (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper touches on the potential risks associated with the use of smart meters in the energy sector, which falls under the category of cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) and potentially also social and information networks (cs.SI).
